#: ../../source/usage.rst:2
msgid "Usage Guide"
msgstr "使用指南"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:4
msgid ""
"The EDAI shell intelligently routes every line you type to the right "
"handler: Tcl commands go to the Tcl interpreter, Python code goes to "
"IPython, and everything else goes to the LLM agent."
msgstr ""
"EDAI shell 智能地将您输入的每一行路由到正确的处理器：Tcl 命令发送到 Tcl 解释器，Python 代码发送到 IPython，其他所有内容发送到 LLM 智能体。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:9
msgid "Direct Tcl Commands"
msgstr "直接输入 Tcl 命令"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:11
msgid "Type any supported Tcl command directly. No ``%tcl`` prefix needed."
msgstr "直接输入任何支持的 Tcl 命令。无需 ``%tcl`` 前缀。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:24
msgid "Tcl commands support variable substitution:"
msgstr "Tcl 命令支持变量替换："

#: ../../source/usage.rst:34
msgid "And command substitution:"
msgstr "以及命令替换："

#: ../../source/usage.rst:42
msgid "Python Commands"
msgstr "Python 命令"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:44
msgid "Any valid Python code is executed directly:"
msgstr "任何有效的 Python 代码都会被直接执行："

#: ../../source/usage.rst:58
msgid "Natural Language (LLM Agent)"
msgstr "自然语言（LLM 智能体）"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:60
msgid ""
"When your input is neither a known Tcl command nor valid Python, it is "
"sent to the LLM agent. The agent interprets your intent and responds with"
" the appropriate EDA commands."
msgstr ""
"当您的输入既不是已知的 Tcl 命令也不是有效的 Python 代码时，它将被发送到 LLM 智能体。智能体会解释您的意图，并以适当的 EDA 命令进行响应。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:74
msgid "The agent remembers conversation context:"
msgstr "智能体会记住对话上下文："

#: ../../source/usage.rst:82
msgid "Using the %tcl Magic"
msgstr "使用 %tcl 魔术命令"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:84
msgid "You can also use the explicit ``%tcl`` IPython magic command:"
msgstr "您也可以使用显式的 ``%tcl`` IPython 魔术命令："

#: ../../source/usage.rst:91
msgid ""
"This is useful when you need to explicitly mark a command as Tcl, or when"
" using Tcl from within Python code cells."
msgstr ""
"当您需要显式地将命令标记为 Tcl，或在 Python 代码单元格中使用 Tcl 时，这非常有用。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:95
msgid "The ask_agent() Function"
msgstr "ask_agent() 函数"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:97
msgid "You can programmatically send messages to the LLM agent from Python code:"
msgstr "您可以通过编程方式从 Python 代码向 LLM 智能体发送消息："

#: ../../source/usage.rst:111
msgid "The run_tcl() Function"
msgstr "run_tcl() 函数"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:113
msgid "Execute Tcl commands from Python code:"
msgstr "从 Python 代码执行 Tcl 命令："

#: ../../source/usage.rst:120
msgid ""
"This is useful when writing Python scripts that mix EDA commands with "
"analysis logic."
msgstr ""
"这在编写混合了 EDA 命令和分析逻辑的 Python 脚本时非常有用。"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:124
msgid "Running a Typical Flow"
msgstr "运行典型流程"

#: ../../source/usage.rst:126
msgid "Here is an example of a complete design flow in EDAI:"
msgstr "以下是在 EDAI 中运行完整设计流程的示例："
